news.snippet: Mohamed Salah has signed a new deal to remain at Liverpool until 2027, ending speculation over his future at Anfield.

news.title: Salah signs contract extension at Liverpool
news.snippet: Liverpool forward Mohamed Salah has signed a contract extension, ending months-long uncertainty over his future at Anfield, the club have announced.

mainNarratives: Mohamed Salah has signed a new contract with Liverpool FC, extending his stay with the club until 2027.
The contract extension ends speculation over Salah's future at Anfield.
Salah has had a remarkable season with Liverpool, contributing significantly to the team.
breakingDevelopments: The signing of the new contract by Mohamed Salah is the most significant recent development.
The contract extension is seen as a positive move for Liverpool FC, ensuring continuity with a key player.
